**Description:** **: This code defines a class named Tools that includes a method for evaluating mathematical equations. The class is initialized with an empty constructor, and the calculator method takes a string equation as input, evaluates it using eval, and returns the result as a string. The purpose is to provide a simple calculator functionality, though it warns against using eval in production due to security risks.

```python
"""
title: Calculator
author: open-webui
author_url: https://github.com/open-webui
